  "description": {
    "zh": "这是最后一个任务，你参不参加？\n\n你要参加？很好！让我们做一些更难的事，你需要用冲锋枪爆头击杀一些目标，确保是近距离。然后用霰弹枪，把一些人从近距离直接变成红雾。小心那些Scav，他们也爱用霰弹枪，祝你好运。",
    "en": "One last task for this, you in or out?\nSounds like you're in, great! Lets do something a little more difficult, you need to land headshots to kill some targets, make sure it's from a short range, and with SMGs. Then use Shotguns, and turn some people into red mist from just a few meters away. And watch out for those bandits, they love using Shotguns too, good luck."
  },
